<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>数据库 - 分类 - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/</link><description>This is my new Hugo FixIt site</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 13:33:32 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Oracle中INSTR、SUBSTR和NVL的用法</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150907-oracle%E4%B8%ADinstrsubstr%E5%92%8Cnvl%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Mon, 07 Sep 2015 16:57:07 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150907-oracle%E4%B8%ADinstrsubstr%E5%92%8Cnvl%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/">数据库</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/oracle/">Oracle</category><description>&lt;p>**INSTR用法：**INSTR(源字符串, 要查找的字符串, 从第几个字符开始, 要找到第几个匹配的序号)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>返回找到的位置，如果找不到则返回0. 默认查找顺序为从左到右。当起始位置为负数的时候，从右边开始查找。若起始位置为0，返回值为0。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>使用MSSQL远程重启服务器的方法</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20121211-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8mssql%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AF%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 Dec 2012 13:56:58 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20121211-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8mssql%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AF%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/">数据库</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/sqlserver/">SQLServer</category><description>&lt;p>单位托管有服务器,或者经常在家里休息时单位服务器出现问题时,相信用远程桌面或&lt;code>pcanywhere&lt;/code>的朋友遇到过莫名其妙断线而不能再连接的情况。这时,如果服务器如果安装有SQL server,则可用如下的方法重启服务器解决。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>常用数据库驱动和JDBC URL</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20121017-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E5%92%8Cjdbc-url/</link><pubDate>Wed, 17 Oct 2012 16:59:53 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20121017-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E5%92%8Cjdbc-url/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/">数据库</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/jdbc/">JDBC</category><description>&lt;h2 id="microsoft-sql-server" class="heading-element">&lt;span>Microsoft SQL Server&lt;/span>
