 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Microsoft SQL Server JDBC Driver （一般用来连接 SQLServer 2000）
驱动程序包名:&lt;code>msbase.jar mssqlserver.jar msutil.jar&lt;/code>
驱动程序类名:&lt;code>com.microsoft.jdbc.sqlserver.SQLServerDriver&lt;/code>
JDBC URL: &lt;code>jdbc:microsoft:sqlserver://&amp;lt;server_name&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;port&amp;gt;&lt;/code>
默认端口1433，如果服务器使用默认端口则port可以省略&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Mysql常用命令行大全</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20120630-mysql%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A8/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Jun 2012 13:01:25 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20120630-mysql%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A8/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/">数据库</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/mysql/">Mysql</category><description>&lt;h2 id="mysql服务的启动和停止" class="heading-element">&lt;span>Mysql服务的启动和停止&lt;/span>
